column5: Hey Art, hope you have a great day....don't forget to dodge the paint balls   What the heck, take the day off and go fishing
Happy B-day Art - enjoy!
Have yourself the bestest day.    Happy Birthday.
happy birthday
Happy Birthday Art !!Are you in the upper or lower age group  Paul
Happy Birthday Art....now get away from the mirror and stop sucking in that gut. Have a great Birthday.

Thanks all for the wishes. I hope that at the age of 49 I can get past the paintball gauntlet with minimum damage. I did not do the birthday sucking in of the gut in front of the mirror thinggy I figured I would take the day off from that. Fishing is planned for the weekend I had too many people who needed plumbing done today to go.  :lol:   Art

You were not 49 last year???  I've often wondered about this and hoping maybe you can answer.....The milkman left his customers with white teeth...what does a plumber leave his customers?       I just wanted to make you smile...please don't answer that question.
You asked here the answer......Slightly poorer.......   Art
Happy B-Day, Art!!!  Have a great one
I thought so....
Happy Birthday Art!
Happy Birthday Arthur! Have a stupendous day!
Have a great day Art.....even if you will be up to your elbows in it....
An early Happy Birthday to my twin brotha from another motha  Have a great one Art!  Joey
Have a super day Art.
Happy Birthday Art .. and remember ... when it comes to paintball, just 'duck and cover' ... or was that 'Tuck and roll'  Well either way have a great day !

Happy Birthday to my twin brother from another Mother! Happy 49th for the first time Art... the two of us have to decide from here forward if we want to increment the counter!  Leah sends a hug as well.. I'm sure that means more than the paragraph above!
Have a great day Art.  S.
Don't go snappin' your suspenders there, Art. Last week I got a hug from Leah for no reason at all!
Happy birthday Art
Happy to ya my brudder from the same mudder.
Yah I meant to talk to you about that... and why my nuts are still sore!
HA!  Hope you're having a great day.
Happy B-Day
